{"tid":1538924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港而家個局面 已經唔係一句撤回條例可以收科","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:57:19.000Z","uid":25797,"like":135,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a205197a298ad902c80c835c7643830df76e481b","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"你6月9號大遊行個晚講撤回條例就真係收到科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到而家呢個環境已經徹底顯示出香港既政治制度係千瘡百孔，今次推冧一條逃犯條例，係呢個政府底下日後只會再有第二第三條既逃犯條例既出現，甚至係廿三條。仲要計返之前既DQ議員、取消參選資格，取締香港民族黨、拒絕FCC馬凱入境、拒發英國金融時報記者簽證、明日大嶼、一地兩檢、沙中線、旺角事件羅織暴動罪名製造政治犯、鉛水事件、721白衣人恐怖襲擊、同埋最重要既係黑警亦然繼續打人，只會越黎越肆無忌憚。今日跪底左，聽日你連生存既機會都唔會再有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n成個香港問題個癥結就係香港民主化既進程，我地要既係徹底改革現有政治制度，有真正既權力制衡 check and balance ，人民能夠用佢既選票改組政府，特首係真正為民服務。咁樣既香港先有重生既一日。<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，呢個政權係用警棍、胡椒噴霧、刀、橡膠子彈、布袋彈、催淚彈、海棉彈、裝甲車、水炮車黎同你講撤回條例同構建對話平台。邊個今日講得些好意須回手，唔好趕狗入窮巷既都係仆街冚家剷，我地要既係香港重光呢一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae82030a528a23c58987668204d0cf93c8baa26","tid":1538924,"uid":290815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7cb246aeb0aebc09ea667c6e8f25f58e5e157b","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3qqGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3qqGn.jpg&h=e0db4b33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e15a318fcb9b8ef057afb339da3cf88a0024824","tid":1538924,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f5b47d62ab53ce98240298fe14801875b7cd53d","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62dc918ee733495f7f6ea9277aafe0cb4d236f5","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92440700a25a20428062cb4e01de1e5c5fb1242d","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9efdc278c58b9eb97b541aa178e5962c0eed35f","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7db6ac767f888fc5ae6066b566dbd5d28917f0d","tid":1538924,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8G0fhW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8G0fhW.jpg&h=5b9edceb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2f70a55fe6b75e66e0d5ac00588cbb7e42e019d","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e