/code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"b5a5aeba5d14704c4b573499ce40c6909337a722","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f06c157038b25709ebdc9f08f8e0abbc3924829","tid":1538924,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太遲了"},{"pid":"149b17fab741cdd08b7aaab9c0d44a6d2b9bee8b","tid":1538924,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1edb1206d250dc35a6781a2c2a97bc26c006c8e","tid":1538924,"uid":196604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a205197a298ad902c80c835c7643830df76e481b","tid":1538924,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"你6月9號大遊行個晚講撤回條例就真係收到科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到而家呢個環境已經徹底顯示出香港既政治制度係千瘡百孔，今次推冧一條逃犯條例，係呢個政府底下日後只會再有第二第三條既逃犯條例既出現，甚至係廿三條。仲要計返之前既DQ議員、取消參選資格，取締香港民族黨、拒絕FCC馬凱入境、拒發英國金融時報記者簽證、明日大嶼、一地兩檢、沙中線、旺角事件羅織暴動罪名製造政治犯、鉛水事件、721白衣人恐怖襲擊、同埋最重要既係黑警亦然繼續打人，只會越黎越肆無忌憚。今日跪底左，聽日你連生存既機會都唔會再有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n成個香港問題個癥結就係香港民主化既進程，我地要既係徹底改革現有政治制度，有真正既權力制衡 check and balance ，人民能夠用佢既選票改組政府，特首係真正為民服務。咁樣既香港先有重生既一日。<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，呢個政權係用警棍、胡椒噴霧、刀、橡膠子彈、布袋彈、催淚彈、海棉彈、裝甲車、水炮車黎同你講撤回條例同構建對話平台。邊個今日講得些好意須回手，唔好趕狗入窮巷既都係仆街冚家剷，我地要既係香港重光呢一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你個位。<br />\n<br />\n我地大家唔好辜負所有付出過，或者已經離開左既義士。 我地係唔會忘記佢地。<br />\n<br />\n我地要贏，贏係要贏晒！唔係輸4球比人！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537433</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中原創《致義士》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fIpRoDyLaws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfIpRoDyLaws&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=a4c4ca61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fIpRoDyLaws</a>"},{"pid":"da8a109dc6bd1f6b950659334dfb34d2904bfec2","tid":1538924,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔撚囉返幾件警畜祭旗 點消心頭之恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2088fdf98bcec9bba56ea868b906070ee9c75b8","tid":1538924,"uid":252884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"四大訴求 咪撚再拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7756d441fed58f866a010489a96330eff9c77df","tid":1538924,"uid":287387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭撤回目標係外國！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n外國少人知有五大訴求，以為香港人成功，林鄭目標係想阻人權法案通過！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔好比佢成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加大國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加大國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加大國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加大國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317eb6fa514ce95a2522409f1a264f5aec66d491","tid":1538924,"ui